text: bmiTell :: (RealFloat a) => a -> a -> String bmiTell weight height | bmi <= skinny = "You're underweight, you emo, you!" | bmi <= normal = "You're supposedly normal. Pffft, I bet you're ugly!" | bmi <= fat = "You're fat! Lose some weight, fatty!" | otherwise = "You're a whale, congratulations!" where bmi = weight / height ~ 2 skinny = 18.5 normal = 25.0 fat = 30.0
